query:
SELECT s.companyName, sr.serviceLevel, sr.rateUsdCents, sr.countryCode, sr.cityId
FROM suppliers s 
JOIN supplierRates sr ON s.id = sr.supplierId 
WHERE sr.countryCode = 'AU' AND sr.serviceType = 'L1_NETWORK'
ORDER BY s.companyName, sr.serviceLevel;
